description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Inner Silence Guided Meditation | Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar' from the channel Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Inner Silence is a powerful guided meditation for healing by Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar. This meditation technique helps you experience the journey from the ceaseless chatter of the mind to the serenity of a still mind.

About #Gurudev: 
World-renowned humanitarian, spiritual leader, and an ambassador of peace and human values. Through his life and work, Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar has inspired millions around the world with a vision of a stress-free and violence-free world. Gurudev founded The Art of Living, a non-profit organization that is engaged in stress-management and service initiatives across the world.
